While most of the students do live on campus, you can find them out and about participating in different activities around the local area of Joplin, Missouri. Ozark Christian College is located in an urban setting. Outside of the central campus they have tons of restaurants in Joplin the students enjoy. It does have religious groups for students to get involved in and help the community. The students, although not having many sports teams, do fully support their teams and have amazing school spirit for their Ambassadors.

Sanader was reelected in the closely contested 2007 parliamentary election.
